Table of Contents  1 Commit Your Changes    There is an official layer called gitbuiltin spacemacs. The git layer is based on magit . Actually, on the magit website, you can always find what you want. This post is a summary of How I use magit in spacemacs.
I like the magit website because of the beautiful font and pleasing color combination.
